00:24:58,347 --> 00:25:01,910
In terms of combat, we moved from a lock-based system

350
00:25:01,910 --> 00:25:06,293
to a full third-person aim system, but also really tried to capture that sense of desperation.

351
00:25:06,293 --> 00:25:09,676
We were rolling Lara back to a point where she was far less confident

352
00:25:09,676 --> 00:25:15,341
and far less competent than people knew her as, and we wanted that to show in her animation and in her mechanics.

353
00:25:15,921 --> 00:25:17,962
And in the case of puzzles, we really

354
00:25:17,962 --> 00:25:21,102
embraced the idea of physics, both for its simulation aspect,

