00:25:24,883 --> 00:25:26,744
with an understanding of cause and effect,

357
00:25:26,744 --> 00:25:29,465
that by using fire and water and mass and pulleys,

358
00:25:29,465 --> 00:25:32,305
we could create environmental challenges that really asked

